34:43.744 --> 34:46.145
(gasps)... New Directions!

34:46.179 --> 34:48.915
Which means the winner of the
National Show Choir Championship

34:48.949 --> 34:50.882
is Throat Explosion!

34:50.918 --> 34:52.885
(crowd cheering)

34:52.920 --> 34:54.920
