41:31.354 --> 41:33.421
Why do you want to know? So
you can steal his dream, too?

41:33.456 --> 41:34.856
- Exactly.
- It's Glee Club.

41:34.890 --> 41:36.091
They've been disbanded.

41:36.125 --> 41:37.892
They didn't win at
nationals; they're turning

41:37.927 --> 41:39.961
